    "homepage": "https://github.com/kwad77/pincher",
    "license": "MIT",
    "notes": [
        "pincher is the binary; pincherMCP refers to the MCP-server mode it exposes by default.",
        "First-run setup:",
        "  pincher init                   # inject usage policy into your CLAUDE.md",
        "  pincher index <repo-path>      # build the index (one-shot CLI mode)",
        "  pincher --http :8080           # or run as a long-lived HTTP server",
        "Set PINCHER_AUTO_RESTART_ON_DRIFT=1 in your MCP launch env if running supervised — see docs/deployment for the full guide."
    ],
    "architecture": {
